Class ValueSet

    ICompositeElement, IElement, IResource, ISupportsUndeclaredExtensions

    public class ValueSet
extends BaseResource
implements IResource
    HAPI/FHIR ValueSet Resource (A set of codes drawn from one or more code systems)

    Definition: A value set specifies a set of codes drawn from one or more code systems

    Requirements:

    Profile Definition: http://hl7.org/fhir/profiles/ValueSet
